                <h4 data-uuid="29eb9a4f85924554ab168c92a5c116ee">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="ff7a11e911bc43128035cd0254587731">The First Continental Congress demanded certain rights from Great Britain.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="a7cf7f3e6a6941b9a19549a14a121abb">First Continental Congress</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="0c45fbaf1d734a77bbc09a2e2e208d7b"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
